description: This file contains a Dart script used for debugging and testing the serialization and deserialization of the Note model object through map and JSON transformations. It constructs a Note, serializes it to JSON, then decodes it back to a Note object, verifying the process.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: A data model representing a note with properties like title, content, timestamps, etc.

methods.name: main
methods.description: Entry point of the script that performs the round-trip serialization and deserialization of a Note object.
